==Finnish==
===Noun===
#loss

[[Category:Finnish nouns]]

===Verb===
#(''slang'') look! ''Kato, tuolla on [[neekeri]]!'' Look, there's a [[negro]]!
#(''slang'') see. ''Kato, ei [[neekeri]] ole haukkumasana.'' See, [[negro]] is not a pejorative word.

A corrupt of ''katso'', imperative case of ''katsoa'', to look.

===Interjection===

#(''slang'') see. ''Se on kato sillä lailla.'' See, that's the way it is.

Also see [[niinku]], [[nääs]], [[tiäksä]]

[[Category:Finnish verbs]]

